        &none  &kp LEFT     &kp UP_ARROW    &kp RIGHT_ARROW  &none     &kp LEFT_GUI      &mt LS(LEFT_CONTROL) NUMBER_4  &kp N5            &kp NUMBER_6  &none
&trans  &none  &kp HOME     &kp DOWN_ARROW  &kp END          &none     &kp LS(LEFT_GUI)  &mt LEFT_ALT NUMBER_1          &kp N2            &kp NUMBER_3  &none  &none
